						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Māṟavarmaṉ (?) Kulaśēkhara I. Year [2]0: A.D. 1268.</hi></p>						

						<p>Much damaged and incomplete. Seems to refer to a grant of land and record an undertaking given by the temple authorities to Sivandakāṟ Perumāḷ of Pākaṉūr-kūṟṟam for offering sacred food to the deity and to undertake repairs to the Mūlasthāṉamuḍaiya Nāyaṉār temple at Teṉ Kallaga-nāḍu.</p>						

